participant_1.name: Emily Johnson
participant_1.personality: Outgoing and adventurous, enjoys sports and being active.
participant_1.background: i live in a three storey house. i enjoy long walks with my dog. i'm a professional tennis player. i am married to a doctor.

participant_2.name: Matthew Clarke
participant_2.personality: Easy-going and curious about the world, loves to explore new cuisines.
participant_2.background: i own a yacht and i rent it out when i am not using it. i've been traveling the world for a years. i also like to cook but i am not very good at it. i've been trying all types of food everywhere i go.
